products.title: Riviera Mix All Light Grey
products.body_html: Built on the new Riviera rubber cupsole, the Riviera Mix All Light Grey introduces classic tones in a contemporary silhouette. It boasts the signature FP Gowtu knot pattern as a monogram on the outsole, adding an exclusive touch. The mix of rubberized leather, nappa, and suede offers elegance and durability, making it ideal for versatile styling.

products.title: Riviera Mix Sky Blue
products.body_html: The Riviera Mix Sky Blue takes inspiration from traditional canvas basketball sneakers, re-imagined with luxury materials. With a blend of rubberized leather, nappa, and suede, this shoe delivers a fresh and vibrant look. The modern Riviera rubber cupsole and Gowtu knot monogram enhance its distinct character, making it a standout in any collection.

products.title: Loafer Gowtu Black / Grey
products.body_html: Immerse yourself in luxury with the Loafer Gowtu Black/Grey, where premium Nappa piping intertwines with a plush Polido leather upper. Inspired by the profound 'Matten-Klopper' ring, this loafer embodies a journey of renewal and the casting off of negativity. Crafted with precision from Cow Polido leather and adorned with a striking Poliéster patch, it encapsulates a perfect harmony of heritage and contemporary style.

products.title: Loafer Gowtu Black / Off White
products.body_html: Immerse yourself in luxury with the Loafer Gowtu Black/Off White, where premium Nappa piping intertwines with a plush Polido leather upper. Inspired by the profound 'Matten-Klopper' ring, this loafer embodies a journey of renewal and the casting off of negativity. Crafted with precision from Cow Polido leather and adorned with a striking Poliéster patch, it encapsulates a perfect harmony of heritage and contemporary style.

products.title: Loafer Bouquet Black
products.body_html: The Loafer Bouquet Black is a truly unique design made from luxury polido leather. Built on a pre-fab leather and rubber sole, it features a clean leather bridge and a removable pin with a hand-made leather bouquet. Each flower is meticulously crafted from fine Italian nappa, making this loafer a standout piece that celebrates artistry and elegance.

products.title: Moc Derby Fuse Black
products.body_html: Step into the future with the Moc Derby Fuse Black, a modern and bulky take on the classic moc derby shoe. Fully re-imagined with new materials, it features a lightweight EVA sole, an upper made from polido leather, and breathable sport mesh lining. The vegan leather micro-quilted diamond collar and detailed embossed two-stripe branding add unique touches, making this shoe perfect for both style and comfort.

products.title: Knit Shirt Gardener Black
products.body_html: Enhance your wardrobe with the Knit Shirt Gardener in Black, a bold, premium jacquard knit piece featuring seasonal floral graphics and a gardener character. Its relaxed fit and breathable fabric make it a standout choice.

products.title: Knit Shorts Gardener Black
products.body_html: Transform your wardrobe with the Knit Short Gardener in Black, a premium jacquard knit short featuring seasonal floral graphics. Designed for comfort with an elastic waistband and drawstring, this relaxed-fit piece is as breathable as it is stylish.

products.title: Knit Shirt Gardener Arona
products.body_html: Revitalize your wardrobe with the Knit Shirt Gardener in Arona, featuring seasonal floral graphics and a gardener character on the chest. This relaxed-fit, button-down shirt combines premium birds-eye jacquard knit with soft breathability.

products.title: Knit Shorts Gardener Arona
products.body_html: Step up your fashion game with the Knit Short Gardener in Arona, a relaxed-fit short crafted from premium birds-eye jacquard knit with seasonal floral graphics. An elastic waistband and drawstring offer comfort in every wear.

products.title: Low Top Suede Organic Off White
products.body_html: The Low Top Suede Organic Off White reflects our origin story, evolving while staying true to its character. Crafted from premium suede leather, it serves as a timeless canvas for seasonal evolution. This classic style is designed to provide comfort and versatility, making it an essential addition to any wardrobe.

products.title: Mondo Suede Organic Off White
products.body_html: The Mondo Suede Organic Off White emphasizes sustainable and traceable materials in its construction. Featuring a premium suede leather upper with mudguards, a heel tab, and understated branding, this timeless sneaker is ideal for eco-conscious individuals seeking style, comfort, and durability in one versatile design.

products.title: Mondo Suede Lux Natural
products.body_html: The Mondo Suede Lux Natural showcases true versatility with a minimalist silhouette and subtle detailing. This timeless sneaker features a premium suede leather upper, complemented by mudguards, a heel tab, and understated branding. A classic design refreshed for the new season, it is perfect for any outfit and occasion.

products.title: Mondo Suede Lux Sky Blue
products.body_html: The Mondo Suede Lux Sky Blue combines timeless style with contemporary detailing. This premium sneaker features a suede leather upper with mudguards, a heel tab, and subtle branding. Its minimalist design ensures versatility, making it a refined addition to your footwear collection, adaptable for any occasion.

products.title: Low Top Ripple Nubuck All Black
products.body_html: You're looking at a design classic. The Low Top was the first Filling Pieces shoe, designed by our founder Guillaume Philibert and has become our signature style. It introduced features like the elongated FP tongue which you tuck your pants behind, and our iconic heel padding which gives a luxury look and makes it extra comfy on your heels.

products.title: Jet Runner Mix Black
products.body_html: Elevate your style with the Jet Runner Mix Black, a refined lightweight runner crafted from soft premium nappa and matte nubuck. With its silver embossed branding, this versatile trainer suits both formal and casual occasions. Experience unmatched comfort and sophistication with this subtly toned design, perfect for completing any outfit effortlessly.

products.title: Sprinter Fussquilt Grey
products.body_html: Inspired by vintage football aesthetics, the Sprinter Fussquilt Grey features quilted detailing and premium goat leather for a soft, comfortable fit. The quilting effect, enhanced by soft goat leather, offers a retro look. Designed with a breathable microfiber lining and a slim rubber cupsole, it balances style with performance, making it ideal for daily wear.

products.title: Sprinter Fussquilt White
products.body_html: Designed with vintage football shoe elements, the Sprinter Fussquilt White is crafted from soft goat leather, offering enhanced padding and quilting. A micro-fiber lining ensures breathability and comfort, while the slim rubber cupsole adds a lightweight feel. Blending old-school athletic charm with modern craftsmanship, this is a timeless addition to any collection.

products.title: Jet Runner Mesh Blue
products.body_html: The Jet Runner Mesh Blue combines luxury and sportiness in a lightweight design, featuring a technical triple-thread mesh. This fresh runner offers all-season appeal, making it an ideal choice for everyday wear. Experience the perfect balance of style and functionality, ensuring your feet stay comfortable and trendy no matter the occasion.

products.title: Jet Runner Nubuck Frost
products.body_html: The Jet Runner Nubuck Frost offers a refined multi-hue aesthetic, showcasing the beauty of soft tones from the FP DNA color palette. This lightweight runner is versatile, making it easy to style with any outfit. Enjoy the blend of fashion and comfort, ensuring you look great and feel even better on any occasion.

products.title: Oryon Cream Grey
products.body_html: The Oryon Cream Grey runner combines an intricate mix of premium leathers, including nubuck, nappa, and crumbs, with technical 3D mesh. This luxurious design features a soft cream color palette, creating an upscale yet sporty look. It’s built on a custom TR sole with an extra-grippy bottom plate and aero-style midsole lines, adding both durability and comfort.

products.title: Low Top Ghost Panel All White
products.body_html: The Low Top Ghost Panel All White brings a fresh twist to a beloved classic. With playful panels in all nubuck and suede, this shoe features an all-white color palette that transitions seamlessly from casual to formal settings. Perfect for everyday wear, this shoe combines style with comfort, ensuring you can tackle any occasion with ease and confidence.

products.title: Mondo Game Light Blue
products.body_html: The Mondo Game Light Blue is a minimalistic sneaker crafted from premium leather uppers. Made from durable nappa and crumbs leather, this versatile shoe combines timeless style with high-quality materials, ensuring you look effortlessly stylish for any occasion.

products.title: T-shirt Dog Walker Arona
products.body_html: Add a playful touch to your wardrobe with the T-shirt Dog Walker in Arona, a regular-fit piece in a rich, washed hue. Featuring the beloved "Dog Walker" graphic, this organic cotton tee blends comfort with a touch of playful character.

products.title: Sweatshirt Dog Walker Arona
products.body_html: Upgrade your essentials with the Sweatshirt Dog Walker in Arona, a boxy crewneck that captures the spirit of the season with a "Dog Walker" graphic. Designed in organic brushed cotton, this sweatshirt offers both comfort and style.

products.title: Sweatshirt Boxy Embroidered Vintage Black
products.body_html: Refresh your wardrobe with the Sweatshirt Boxy Embroidered in Vintage Black, a boxy crewneck designed with a washed, vintage finish for an effortlessly cool aesthetic. Featuring a 3D Gowtu embroidered logo and FP branded neck stitching, this piece combines refined details with timeless style. Made from 100% organic cotton, it delivers the perfect balance of comfort and sophistication. A versatile staple that’s as easy to wear as it is to love.

products.title: Pants Core Link Vintage Black
products.body_html: The Pants Core Link in Vintage Black offers a modern fit, defined by soft pleats and a subtle vintage wash. Made from 100% cotton, the fabric has a natural texture that enhances its timeless character. An elastic waistband ensures everyday comfort without compromising on style.

products.title: Coach Jacket Logo Black
products.body_html: Enhance your wardrobe with the Coach Jacket Logo Black, a timeless piece that combines a classic fit with premium craftsmanship for both formal and casual occasions. Featuring a versatile double zipper, this jacket offers multiple styling options, adding sophistication to any look. Crafted for durability and comfort.

products.title: Coach Pants Logo Black
products.body_html: Step up your fashion game with the Coach Pants Logo Black, a versatile piece crafted for both formal and casual settings. With a premium fabric and structured seam, these pants offer a balance of elegance and relaxed comfort. Made from 85% cotton, 13% polyester, and 2% elastane for lasting wear and style.

products.title: Coach Jacket Antique White
products.body_html: Upgrade your outerwear with the Coach Jacket Antique White, a classic-fit piece in premium fabric for both casual and formal looks. Its double zipper design allows for multiple styling options, blending practicality with sophistication.
